<i>noun</i>: 화평 [화평], 화친 [화친], 화목 [화목], 평화 [평화], 태평 [태평], 안녕 [안녕], 무사태평 [무사태평] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>화평 [화평]</dt><br>
<dd>1. peace; harmony</dd><br>
<dd>마음속이나 사람들 사이에 갈등이 없이 평화로움.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one is mentally peaceful or lives at peace with others without any conflict.</dd><br>
<dd>2. peace; harmony</dd><br>
<dd>나라 사이에 충돌이나 전쟁이 없이 평화로움.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which two or more countries are at peace with each other without any conflict or war.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>화친 [화친]</dt><br>
<dd>amity; friendship; peace</dd><br>
<dd>나라와 나라 사이에 싸움이 없이 서로 가까이 지냄.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which two or more countries are on good terms, without any fighting.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>화목 [화목]</dt><br>
<dd>harmony; concord; peace</dd><br>
<dd>서로 뜻이 맞고 정다움.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of agreeing with each other and being friendly toward each other.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>평화 [평화]</dt><br>
<dd>1. peace</dd><br>
<dd>걱정이나 탈이 없이 조용하고 화목함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being quiet and harmonious, free from worries or troubles.</dd><br>
<dd>2. peace</dd><br>
<dd>전쟁이나 다툼 등의 갈등이 없이 조용하고 화목함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being quiet and harmonious, free from conflicts such as war, fighting, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>태평 [태평]</dt><br>
<dd>1. peace</dd><br>
<dd>나라가 안정되어 아무 걱정이나 탈이 없음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a nation being peaceful without worries or troubles.</dd><br>
<dd>2. tranquility</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 아무 걱정이 없음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of one's mind being serene without worries or troubles.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>안녕 [안녕]</dt><br>
<dd>peace; good health</dd><br>
<dd>아무 문제나 걱정이 없이 편안함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being comfortable with no worry nor problem.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>무사태평 [무사태평]</dt><br>
<dd>1. peace; tranquility</dd><br>
<dd>아무런 문제나 걱정거리가 없이 편안함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being peaceful without any problem or worry.</dd><br>
<dd>2. optimism</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 심각하게 생각하지 않아 근심이나 걱정이 없음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of having no worry or concern because one does not think seriously of a matter.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>